Leonardo at Milanello: &quot;We've never thought about changing Gattuso, there is no plan to change him. No other coaches have been contacted from Milan.&quot; [@SimoNobilini]<br />
Leonardo: &quot;Transfer market? It will be a market of opportunities, no crazy spending. UEFA called us after the purchase of Paquet&aacute;, so we could not move forward in the transfer market. They have warned us.&quot;<br />
Leonardo on Higuain: &quot;My relationship with him is very direct, he has a very important role for us, and he knows it. We have never had any doubts about Higuain; no requests from Chelsea, nor has he asked to leave.&quot;

Leonardo: &quot;Qualification to the Champions League is fundamental, the 4th place is linked to the redemption of Higuain and Bakayoko.&quot;<br />
<br />
Maldini: &quot;We are absolutely convinced of being able to get the 4th place. Higuain? His leadership is not in questions; it is a new situation for him. The redemptions? With the players, we've been clear to them that Champions League qualification is compulsory.&quot;

